               <p>I lost my handkerchief on Tuesday last at <placeName id="t17850914-84-crimeloc421">Saint Andrew's church, Holborn</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17850914-84-crimeloc421" type="placeName" value="Saint Andrew's church, Holborn"></interp>
